---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Contact - The Menon Lab">
  <article class="contact-page">
    <h1>Contact</h1>
    
    <section>
      <p>
        Have a question, suggestion, or want to collaborate? I'd love to hear from you.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="contact-methods">
      <div class="contact-card">
        <h2>üìß Email</h2>
        <p>Best for detailed inquiries, collaborations, or consulting requests.</p>
        <a href="mailto:prahlad.menon@quant.md" class="contact-link">prahlad.menon@quant.md</a>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-card">
        <h2>üêô GitHub</h2>
        <p>Found a bug or want to contribute? Open an issue or PR.</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/menonpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="contact-link">github.com/menonpg</a>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-card">
        <h2>üåê Website</h2>
        <p>Learn more about my work and other projects.</p>
        <a href="https://themenonlab.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="contact-link">themenonlab.com</a>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-card">
        <h2>üê¶ X (Twitter)</h2>
        <p>Follow for quick updates and AI/ML discussions.</p>
        <a href="https://x.com/themedcave" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="contact-link">@themedcave</a>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-card">
        <h2>ü§ñ Reddit</h2>
        <p>AI discussions and community posts.</p>
        <a href="https://reddit.com/u/the_ai_scientist" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="contact-link">u/the_ai_scientist</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>What I Can Help With</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>AI/ML Consulting</strong> ‚Äî Strategy, architecture, implementation</li>
        <li><strong>Technical Writing</strong> ‚Äî Guest posts, documentation, tutorials</li>
        <li><strong>Speaking</strong> ‚Äî Podcasts, webinars, conferences</li>
        <li><strong>Collaboration</strong> ‚Äî Open source projects, research partnerships</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Response Time</h2>
      <p>
        I typically respond to emails within 1-2 business days. For urgent matters, 
        please mention "URGENT" in the subject line.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .contact-page {
    max-width: 42rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h1 {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .contact-methods {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .contact-card {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: var(--bg-secondary, rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.05));
  }

  .contact-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .contact-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .contact-link {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .contact-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }

  ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
